                                                </section>
                                            
    <section class="page-1 section-7 sr-story-main" id="909617">
        <article class="sr-story clearfix" data-id="909617" data-url="/speedreads/909617/gianna-bryant-teammates-selected-honorary-wnba-draftees" data-headline="Gianna Bryant, teammates selected as honorary WNBA draftees" data-tags="[speedread,News]" data-publish-date="April 18, 2020" data-authors="[Tim O'Donnell]">
            
            
                            <div class="sr-slug"><a href="/speedreads/section/Rest%20in%20peace">Rest in peace</a></div>
            
            <div class="sr-headline-section">
                <div class="edit-link">
	<a href="http://cms.theweek.com/admin/tw-admin/edit/909617">Edit</a>
</div>                <h2 class="sr-headline"><a href="/speedreads/909617/gianna-bryant-teammates-selected-honorary-wnba-draftees">Gianna Bryant, teammates selected as honorary WNBA draftees</a></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="sr-date">April 18, 2020</div>

            <div class="sr-body-share-wrapper">
                <div class="sr-body" id="sr-body-909617">
                    
                    <div class="sr-text">
                         <p>The WNBA <a href="https://www.cbssports.com/wnba/news/2020-wnba-draft-gianna-bryant-teammates-in-fatal-helicopter-crash-selected-as-honorary-draft-picks/" target="_blank">paid tribute</a> to the late Gianna Bryant on Friday night, making her and two of her youth basketball teammates — Alyssa Altobelli and Payton Chester — honorary draftees.</p>
<p>The 13-year-old Bryant was killed alongside Altobelli, Chester, her father Kobe Bryant, and five others in a helicopter crash in California in January. The elder Bryant was a superstar for the NBA's Los Angeles Lakers, and his daughter certainly looked like she was going to follow in his footsteps and achieve her dream of playing in the WNBA. Gianna's mother, Vanessa Bryant, thanked the WNBA for the gesture.</p>
<p></p><center>
<blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr" xml:lang="en">"Work hard. Never settle. Use that Mamba Mentality."</p>
<p>Vanessa Bryant thanks the WNBA for honoring Gigi, and shares some wisdom for the 2020 draft class. <a href="https://t.co/CwvyxqG0fi">pic.twitter.com/CwvyxqG0fi</a></p>
<p>— ESPN (@espn) <a href="https://twitter.com/espn/status/1251289390653079552?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">April 17, 2020</a></p></blockquote>
<script async="" src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script><p></p></center>
<p>The league also <a href="https://www.cbssports.com/wnba/news/2020-wnba-draft-gianna-bryant-teammates-in-fatal-helicopter-crash-selected-as-honorary-draft-picks/" target="_blank">announced</a> it's creating the "Kobe and Gigi Bryant WNBA Advocacy Award," which will be given to a player who makes contributions to the visibility, perception, and advancement of girls and women's basketball, CBS Sports reports.</p>
<p>In the official draft, which was held virtually because of the novel COVID-19 coronavirus pandemic, the New York Liberty <a href="https://www.espn.com/wnba/story/_/id/29050519/oregon-superstar-sabrina-ionescu-goes-no-1-new-york-liberty" target="_blank">selected</a> University of Oregon star Sabrina Ionescu with the no. 1 overall pick. Ionescu had a prolific career for the Ducks, compiling an NCAA-record 26 triple-doubles over her four years in Eugene. She's also the first player in men's or women's basketball to record more than 2,000 points, 1,000 rebounds, and 1,000 assists. Ionescu <a href="https://www.sportingnews.com/us/nba/news/sabrina-ionescu-kobe-bryant-friendship-timeline/1drj26q6mgrku1jh9emw75gwri" target="_blank">had</a> a close relationship with both Kobe, whom she considered a mentor, and Gianna Bryant. Read more at <a href="https://www.espn.com/wnba/story/_/id/29050519/oregon-superstar-sabrina-ionescu-goes-no-1-new-york-liberty" target="_blank">ESPN</a> and <a href="https://www.cbssports.com/wnba/news/2020-wnba-draft-gianna-bryant-teammates-in-fatal-helicopter-crash-selected-as-honorary-draft-picks/" target="_blank">CBS Sports</a>. <a class="author" href=/authors/tim-odonnell><em>Tim O'Donnell</em></a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="speedreads-share-section sr-909617">
                    <span class="fb sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909617/gianna-bryant-teammates-selected-honorary-wnba-draftees" data-text="Gianna Bryant, teammates selected as honorary WNBA draftees"></span>
                    <span class="twitter sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909617/gianna-bryant-teammates-selected-honorary-wnba-draftees" data-text="Gianna Bryant, teammates selected as honorary WNBA draftees" ></span>
                    <a class="email sr-social-btn" href="mailto:?subject=Gianna Bryant, teammates selected as honorary WNBA draftees&amp;body=https://theweek.com/speedreads/909617/gianna-bryant-teammates-selected-honorary-wnba-draftees" title="Share by Email" aria-label="Share by Email"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

                                                        <div class="end-of-story-ad dfp-ad page-1-sr-7">
                         
    <div id="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3-desktop" class="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3 managed-ad dfp-ad desktop"
        data-ad-id="sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3"
        data-device="desktop"
        data-targets="name:sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3;position:6;placement:TW_SR_D_6;inventory:btf;breakpoint:desktop;tags:speedread,News;"
                >
    </div>

    <div id="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3-tablet" class="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3 managed-ad dfp-ad tablet"
        data-ad-id="sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3"
        data-device="tablet"
        data-targets="name:sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3;position:6;placement:TW_SR_T_6;inventory:btf;breakpoint:tablet;tags:speedread,News;"
                >
    </div>

    <div id="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3-mobile" class="sr-end-of-story-leaderboard-3 managed-ad dfp-ad mobile"
        data-ad-id="sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3"
        data-device="mobile"
        data-targets="name:sr_end_of_story_leaderboard_3;position:6;placement:TW_SR_M_6;inventory:btf;breakpoint:mobile;tags:speedread,News;"
